node.text:
Today is the day! The new iconic @otam_custom_projects 70HT is ready to wow 
the Cannes Yachting Festival 2021 (Yacht Position LE QUAI MAX LAUBEUF
QML089)… because the new OTAM 70HT is the epitome of the dynamic 
performance and timeless style that has made the iconic Italian brand instantly 
recognizable around the world. Tag people you would invite on board!
